Function to create raw child antropometry dataset

Source: R/03-recode_anthro.R
create_canthro.Rd

Function to create raw child antropometry dataset

create_canthro(df, x)

Arguments

df

A data.frame collected for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Study containing child anthropometry data
x

A data.frame collected for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Study containing identifying information that will be linked to the child anthropometry data

Value

A data.frame containing raw child anthropometry data for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Study

Examples

create_canthro(df = childAnthro, x = anthroDF)
